 align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uhaldainas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haldainas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 115<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/14/02 10:47:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3215.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Upgrading my weapons with 80K?</span><hr size=1> Fleshgrinder is the best aggro weap out of all 4..but also with 80k you could possibly afford wavecrasher and sboz, which will be close to the same as fleshgrinder + ornate sword. But seeing as you already have Ornate sword, id say just get the fleshgrinder <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7808 target="_blank"><img src=http://haldainas.0catch.com/Opt-Hald-Sig.jpg border=0></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ucslochraven.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CSLochraven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 93<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/14/02 3:01:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3215.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://gs.cdnow.com/graphics/COVERART/local/L/80/01/00138001.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Upgrading my weapons with 80K?</span><hr size=1> If you want to go the aggro route...Wavecrasher and Fleshgrinder.  That'd be my choice. <p><b>Lochraven<b><br>Myrmidon<br>The Nameless</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title>