with 80K?</span><hr size=1> I'd skip the wavecrasher.  For the price it just isn't worth it.  Sure the proc is nice, but 9/19 with no hps, ac or stamina on the weapon is just terrible.  I'd say that you should pick up either the horn or swiftblade of zek.  I haven't used a horn, but I use my SBoZ all the time and never have problems with agro.  Plus you can't beat 100 hps with other stats from a weapon.  <br><br>If you really want a wavecrasher you should get some friends and camp SG.  With a full group of 55-60 types you can mow down the sirens and you'll get a ton of quest gems too.  In three trips to SG so far I have seen the wavecrasher mob each time.  Once she dropped the Drums of the Beast, once wavecrasher, and once some pally/sk shield.  Anyway I guess my point is that it is a lot easier to get a wavecrasher single group than it is to get a horn or swiftblade :P<br><br>Gartuff<br>Level 60 Warlord<br>Rallos Zek<br>&lt;Ex Tempore&gt;   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/unayl7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nayl7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/16/02 9:14:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3215.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Upgrading my weapons with 80K?</span><hr size=1> Well, I wound up stumbling across good deals for a wavecrasher and a SBoZ within a day of each other, so now I have both of them.  At this point, Im thinking about selling the Wavecrasher and the LSOEE and picking up a Frostbringer for my off hand.  The people with Fleshgrinders for sale are currently living in never never land on my server as far as their prices go, and it seems like the drop rate must be reasonable given the number of em I'm seeing in circulation.   <p>Nayl <BR> Proud member of the Tunare strap-on club</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubamilbanebringer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bamil Banebringer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/16/02 11:14:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3215.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Upgrading my weapons with 80K?</span><hr size=1> Sup Nayl -<br><br>I recently picked up a fleshgrinder and sboz. Before that I was using the sboz/frosty combo and was fairly pleased. I will say on the fleshgrinder that while it procs alot it doesn't seem to generate the aggro I expected, but I'm not complaining.<br><br>I'm working to pick up a horn to replace the sboz, or maybe I'll just get lucky and finally get Sev.<br><br>See you in game bud. <p>-BamBam59 MyrmidonSpirit Guardians</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=3215.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3215.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=3215.topic><img src